    • Constructor Detail

      • WebFile

        public WebFile(String urlString)
        throws MalformedURLException,
               IOException
        Open a web file. Various assumptions include:
        • The URL protocol is HTTP
        • IF no charset is specified by the response header, it is assumed to be DEFAULT_CHARSET_ENCODING.
        Throws:
        MalformedURLException
        IOException
